					Full Description



		Anshu's Clothing Limited is an India-based company, which is engaged in the retail sale of readymade garments. The Company is involved in the made-ups of textiles. The Company operates Anshu's Designer Studio, which is a fashion house and designer boutique in Ahmedabad. The Company, through Anshu's Designer Studio, offers a range of products, which include Indian ethnic wear, Indian wedding saris, wedding bridal saris, evening wear, party wear and Indian designer wear. Its collection includes Designer Sarees, designer Salwar Kameez, Bridal Collection as Bridal Sarees and Bridal Lehnga, party wear lehenga and party wear sarees. The Company offers kids wear under the LOLIPOP brand. Its Kalamkari brand offers middle class to high class women's wear. The Company operates through brand outlets for trading of readymade garments.
» Full Overview of ANSU.BO







